    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi regnante domino <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21">Berengario</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rege</rs> hic in Italia. anno nono decimo. sub die
                        primo mense septenbrio indicione . . . . . feliciter. Dilectissimo atque
                        amantissimo michi semper <persName key="#Alemannus #friendshipFor"
                            ref="#people/165">Ingelfredus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Alemannus">ex genere Alemannorum</rs> qui habitaturus <geogName
                            key="#Fines" ref="#estates/504"><rs key="#Fines">in fine
                                Furvulanense</rs>
                        </geogName><rs key="#friendshipFor">amicus meus michi fideliter servire
                        </rs> visus est. Ego in Dei nomini omnipotentis <persName
                            key="#Bishops #friendshipFor" ref="#people/123">Adelardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">venerapilis episcopus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/503"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >sancte Veronensis ecclesie </rs></orgName><rs key="#friendshipFor"
                            >amicus </rs>et donator tuus presens et presentibus dixi. scribere
                        previdi dilectionis tue ex meo dono et consensu atque concedo et trado tibi
                        infrascripto Ingelfredo concedere atque confirmare visus sum a presenti die
                        et hora ad proprietatem tuam habendum idest in integrum omnibus rebus illis
                            <rs>quas michi advenit </rs>a <persName key="#nephewOf"
                            ref="#people/623">Wicherio </persName>et site sunt ipse res <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/514"><rs key="#Comitatus">in comitatu
                                Montisiligano </rs></geogName>seu in <geogName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Curtes #Domuscultae #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Decima #Aldius #Slave"
                            ref="#estates/515"><placeName
                                key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Curtes #Domuscultae #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Decima #Aldius #Slave"
                                ref="#places/911">Cona </placeName></geogName>aut <geogName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Curtes #Domuscultae #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Decima #Aldius #Slave"
                            ref="#estates/516"><placeName
                                key="#Rivers #Curtes #Domuscultae #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Decima #Aldius #Slave"
                                ref="#places/912">in Montagnana</placeName>
                        </geogName>seu in <geogName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Curtes #Domuscultae #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Decima #Aldius #Slave"
                            ref="#estates/517"><placeName
                                key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Curtes #Domuscultae #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Decima #Aldius #Slave"
                                ref="#places/913">Petriolo</placeName>
                        </geogName>vel per singula loca in suprascripto comitatu Montisilicano tam
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curtis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Domuscultae">domi cultis </rs><rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >massariciis </rs>de <rs key="#Wine">vineis </rs>vero tam de <rs
                            key="#Cereals">terris aratoris seu agris</rs>. <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>. <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>. <rs>pascuis</rs>. <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>. saletis.<rs key="#Rivers"> rivis </rs>ac <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>. <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscationibus et aquario</rs>. <rs key="#Decima">decima</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">pensionibus</rs>. <rs
                            key="#Slave">servis vel ancillis</rs>. <rs key="#Aldius">aldiis vel
                            aldianas</rs>. mobiles vel inmobiles cum onmi et ex omnibus ut sepe dixi
                        si quid mihi pertinet habere de infrascripto Wicherio nepote meo advenit a
                        presenti die et ora quantum michi ibidem legibus pertinet et pertinere debet
                        dono. contrado tibi infrascriptus Ingelfredus et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">proprietatem</rs> illam in Cona que fuit
                            <persName key="#nephewOf" ref="#people/624">Everardo </persName><rs
                            key="#nephewOf">nepote meo</rs> sicut ad ipsum infrascriptum Everardo
                        Wicherio fuit possessor. et exinde michi de omnia qualiter superius legitur
                        ad te infrascriptus Ingelfredus susceptore michi acceptabile launechild
                        manicias par unum. ut presens mea donacio qualiter superius legitur omnique
                        tempore firma et stabile permaneat quam ipse qui supra Adelardus episcopus
                        qui pergamena et atramento et pinna manibus suis de terra levavit et mihi
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Simpertus">Simperto</name>
                        </persName><rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> tradidit ad scribendum et testes
                        subter ad roborandum optulit et inconvulsa et irrevocabilis debeat permanere
                        cum stipulacione subnixa quam vero donacionis cartulam <placeName
                            ref="#places/59">Verona</placeName>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/508"><rs key="#Fines">fine
                            </rs>Gardense</geogName> feliciter. Ego <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/123">Adelardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/503">sancte Veronensis <rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        </orgName>hanc cartulam donacionis a me facta subscripsi. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Alemannus #sonOf"><name ref="Sinibaldus">Sinibaldo
                            </name></persName><rs key="#Witness #Alemannus">ex Alamannorum genere
                            </rs><rs key="#sonOf">filius</rs> bone memorie <persName key="#fatherOf"
                                ><rs key="#fatherOf"><name ref="Teobaldus de Salto">Tebaldo de
                                    Saltus</name></rs>.</persName>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Alemannus #sonOf"><name ref="Ingo">Ingoni
                            </name></persName><rs key="#Witness #Alemannus #sonOf">filius eius ex
                            Alamanno</rs>. <persName key="#Witness #Alemannus #sonOf"><name
                                ref="Todelbertus">Todelbertus</name>
                        </persName><rs key="#Witness #Alemannus #sonOf">ex Alemannorum genere filius
                                </rs><persName><name ref="Walterius">Walterii.</name></persName>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Salian" ref="#people/625">Milo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Salian">ex genere Francorum</rs>. <persName key="#Witness #sonOf"
                                ><name ref="Petrus">Petri </name></persName><rs key="#sonOf">filius
                            </rs><persName key="#fatherOf"><name ref="Adalbertus"><rs
                                    key="#fatherOf">Adelberti.</rs></name></persName>
                        <persName key="#Witness #sonOf"><name ref="Alticherius"
                            >Alticherio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#sonOf">filius</rs><persName key="#fatherOf">
                            <name ref="Dominicus"><rs key="#fatherOf"
                            >Dominico</rs></name></persName>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/512"><rs key="#Comitatus">ex
                                comitatu Ceneza.</rs></geogName>
                        <persName key="#Witness #sonOf"><name ref="Walmannus">Walmanno
                            </name></persName><rs key="#sonOf">filius</rs><persName>
                            <name ref="Luvodus de Trento">Luvodo de Trento </name></persName><rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Ego <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Simpertus ">Simpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> qui hanc paginam scripsi et post traditam
                        conplevi et roboravi. Egoque <persName key="#Notary #Causidicus"><name
                                ref="Adam">Adam</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary #Causidicus">notarius et causidicus</rs> hoc exemplum ex
                        autentico renovavi ne causa vetustatis consumeretur et quod inibi vidi et
                        legi scripsi conplevi et dedi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
